'''''Aeromonas phage phiO18P''''' is a [[virus]] of the family [[Myoviridae]], genus ''[[Hp1likevirus]]''.<ref>[[International Committee on Taxonomy of Viruses]] (ICTV) [http://talk.ictvonline.org/files/ictv_documents/m/msl/4090.aspx Master Species List of 2011, version 2].</ref>

